tip.text: The view is amazing... Check the sunset time when planning to go there to be there at time...
Great movie night with happy hour beers and very nice double burger...
Many food stalls with wide variety of meals. Order one to share and then pick another stall to enjoy more tastes...

venue.name: Chinatown Food Street (牛車水美食街)

tip.text: Best minced meat noodles (dry) in Singapore. Also awarded by Michelin star. Get ready for 1 hour waiting in a queue...

venue.name: Hill Street Tai Hwa Pork Noodle

tip.text: Best view in Kuala Lumpur. Go to the top floor first to enjoy open air view and then take your time and explore the surroundings with binoculars in lower floor...
Great wontons, beef soup, noodles and xiaolongbao...

venue.name: Din Tai Fung (Din Tai Fung (鼎泰豐))

tip.text: Surprisingly very nice sushi dishes despite the venue is located in shopping mall. All tastes were as they should be. Very friendly staff...

formattedAddress: Beachwalk, Lt. 2 Blok C #14,15,16 (Jalan Pantai Kuta)

tip.text: Little bit pricey restaurant but definatelly worth it. Pork or beef ribs for IDR135.000, Mie Goreng with small spare ribs for IDR79.000, large Bintang for IDR49.000. Wifi password: 12345678

venue.name: Iga Warung BBQ RIB HOUSE & Indonesian food

tip.text: Krasne misto. Nejlepsi domaci dorty siroko daleko. Skvela obsluha a vynikajici kava.

venue.name: Václav Havel Airport Prague (PRG) (Letiště Václava Havla Praha)

tip.text: When serious about meat, this is the place...
Sklo, papir, plast, elektroodpad, pouzite obleceni.
